            <description><![CDATA[减肥神速的生酮饮食，靠谱吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>🙅🏻♂️别瞎搞！<br><br>生酮饮食就是低碳+中等蛋白+高脂，吃富含脂肪（蛋、畜禽肉、鱼虾肉、坚果等）的食物吃到饱，脂肪代谢会生成酮体，所以叫“生酮饮食”，但这种饮食方式其实是治疗性饮食，想减肥的宝子们，阿卫建议：别碰！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视网）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj66hsyc4bj20tp99ub29.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
